snippet.title: GAROU: MARK OF THE WOLVES (Neo Geo) - Intro / Opening
snippet.description:
Intro cutscenes of Garou: Mark of the Wolves (Neo Geo).

0:00 - Intro 1
1:09 - Geese Intro

Certainly, they existed...
Those blinded by ambition. 
Those consumed with vengeance.
But here they do not exist.
Only winners and losers here.
For here, THE MIGHTY RULE.

Garou Playthroughs: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL_YL558gxlL_xuXqXCw_ng_prPMEv_rdb
